label: FE599NX
info_overview: Camelot style residential keypad deadbolt door lock and lever.
info_inclusion:
1. Enter 6 digit Programming Code
  2. Wait for Schlage button to blink 3 times and 3 beeps
  3. Press the Schlage button and then 0

On Success the Schlage button will blink with no beeps.
info_exclusion:
1. Enter 6 digit Programming Code
  2. Wait for Schlage button to blink 3 times and 3 beeps
  3. Press the Schlage button and then 0
category_description: Devices whose primary pupose is locking something

parameters.label: Lock Basic Set Value
parameters.description: Byte to send with set command to devices in association group 1

associations.label: Basic Set
associations.description: Basic Set sent with set command (configuration parameter 7)

associations.label: Device Status
associations.description: All associated commands are sent to the nodes in this group

commandclass.name: NO_OPERATION
commandclass.label: No Operation - used for PINGing a device.

channels.name: alarm_raw
channels.label: Alarm (raw)
channels.overview:
